      },
      localw: {
        img: "https://cataas.com/cat/says/LocalW?size=50&color=white",
        title: "LocalW",
        desc: `LocalW, kedi dÃ¼nyasÄ±nÄ±n en troll Ã¼yesi. Sosyal becerileri az, bazen komik davranÄ±ÅŸlar sergiler. 
